OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,FPaedophile singer Ian Watkins was
OL,7,Fbullied for money and received letters
OL,8,Fthreatening he would get his "head
OL,9,Fcracked open" days before he was
OL,10,Fstabbed to death, a court heard.
OL,12,FThe disgraced Lostprophets frontman
OL,13,Fwas serving 29 years for child sex
OL,14,Foffences when he was fatally attacked
OL,15,Fin his cell at HMP Wakefield on 11
OL,16,FOctober last year.
OL,18,FFellow prisoners Rico Gedel, 25, and
OL,19,F44-year-old Samuel Dodsworth deny
OL,20,Fmurder and are on trial at Leeds Crown
OL,21,FCourt.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@MO]
