OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,FOn the second day of proceedings the
OL,7,Fjury heard from prison officer Simon
OL,8,FRothwell, who said he was "vulnerable"
OL,9,Fbecause other prisoners "knew he had
OL,10,Fmoney".
OL,12,FIn a statement read to the court by
OL,13,Fprosecutor Chris Rose, the officer
OL,14,Fsaid: "He was quite a high-profile
OL,15,Fprisoner as he was quite well-known
OL,16,Fprior to him being sentenced.
OL,18,F"I worked on C wing at the time.
OL,19,FWatkins had been on that particular
OL,20,Fwing for approximately 10 years.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@fO]qD@YOUrD@FO]vD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
