OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,F"I built up a good rapport with
OL,7,FWatkins ` he seemed to have built up a
OL,8,Ftrust in me and would disclose
OL,9,Finformation that I could report back
OL,10,Fon.
OL,12,F"Watkins has always been vulnerable,
OL,13,Fbeing bullied for money, as people
OL,14,Fwere aware of his history and knew he
OL,15,Fhad money."
OL,17,FMr Rothwell said Watkins, of Merthyr
OL,18,FTydfil in Wales, had told him on 10
OL,19,FOctober that he had recently received
OL,20,Ftwo "quite threatening" letters.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@KO]|D@EOU|D@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
