OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,FHis statement continued: "I told him I
OL,7,Fwould come down to the wing and see
OL,8,Fhim and recover the letters.
OL,10,F"I took a distraction pack, which is
OL,11,Fbasically a colouring-in book, so it
OL,12,Fwould look to anyone that saw that I
OL,13,Fwas dropping this off."
OL,15,FAfter taking the letters, the officer
OL,16,Fsaid he contacted Watkins by the in-
OL,17,Fcell phone and "advised that he should
OL,18,Fself-isolate in his own cell for the
OL,19,Fweekend".
OL,26,@nD@ZOUrD@AOUuD@WO]yD@POU{D@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
