OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,FMr Rothwell's statement said: "I rang
OL,7,FWatkins and told him my advice, but he
OL,8,Freplied and said 'no I think I'll be
OL,9,FOK.'"
OL,11,FThe officer said following the
OL,12,Fconversation, he told staff of his
OL,13,F"concerns" and to do "extra patrols
OL,14,Fand extra checks".
OL,16,FThe prosecutor then read out the two
OL,17,Fletters Watkins received, with one
OL,18,Fsaying: "Ian, you've got until
OL,19,FSaturday to pay for my Hi-Fi, lamp and
OL,20,Ffan.
OL,26,@nD@_OUqD@EO]uD@AOUuD@JO]uD@VOUvD@QO]zD@
OL,26,AIOU
