OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,F"If you don't pay by then, I promise
OL,7,Fyou, I will get your head cracked
OL,8,Fopen, you snitch.
OL,10,F"Give a number so my boy can message
OL,11,Fyour people to get my bank details to
OL,12,Fput in #500.
OL,14,F"If it's not done by Saturday, you
OL,15,Fwill see what will happen to you...
OL,16,FThis is your last chance."
OL,18,FThe court heard that the second note
OL,19,Fcontained similar content, with the
OL,20,Fmessage beginning: "You snitch, you
OL,21,Fgot me kicked off the wing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@ZO]|D@TOU
