OL,3,CIan Watkins 'bullied for cash' before
OL,4,Cfatal stabbing, trial told
OL,6,FJurors have previously heard Watkins,
OL,7,Fwho was jailed in December 2013, was
OL,8,Fstabbed three times in the head and
OL,9,Fneck.
OL,11,FProsecutors say Dodsworth acted as a
OL,12,Flookout while Gedel carried out the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,FAs well as murder both men deny
OL,16,Fpossession of a knife in prison.
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
